  "texts": [
    "First, educational institutions should promote the use of Chat GPT while ensuring that it is used in an inclusive, equitable, transparent, and ethical manner.",
    "Second, assessment standards should be revised to prevent unfair learning assessment, and formative assessment should be given priority over summative assessment.",
    "Third, educational institutions should train and guide teachers and students on how to effectively use Chat GPT while maintaining academic integrity.",
    "Fourth, action research should be conducted to further investigate the effectiveness and efficiency of integrating Chat GPT into education, and funding should be allocated to research the use of AI tools for educational purposes.",
    "Fifth, students should be vigilant in using Chat GPT and review and analyze the responses generated by the tool to ensure accuracy and compliance with academic integrity policies."
  ],
